<% layout('layouts/layout') -%>
<% block('header', true) %>
<% block('sidebar', true) %>
<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-8">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-6 flex items-center">
    <i class="fas fa-question-circle mr-2"></i> Help &amp; Guide
  </h1>
  <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What is this system?</h2>
      <p>This is a personal portfolio and resume management system. You can add, edit, and organize your experiences, projects, skills, certifications, education, and media files. The system provides both an admin dashboard and public-facing portfolio pages.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How to use the dashboard?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Login as admin to access the dashboard.</li>
        <li>Use the sidebar to navigate between sections: Experience, Projects, Skills, Certifications, Education, Media, Personal Info, and Settings.</li>
        <li>Each section allows you to add, edit, and delete entries. Use the "Add New" button to create new items.</li>
        <li>For images and files, use the integrated Media Manager to upload and select files.</li>
        <li>Settings page lets you update your profile and change your password.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Tips</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Keep your profile and portfolio up to date for best results.</li>
        <li>Use high-quality images for projects and skills.</li>
        <li>Organize your media files into folders for easy management.</li>
        <li>If you forget your password, contact the system administrator.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Need more help?</h2>
      <p>Contact support or refer to the documentation for advanced usage and troubleshooting.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
